I didn't get the joke - No agarré el chiste 
That film gets me every time - Esa película me conmueve.
I got him a new camera - Le compré una nueva cámara
We got drunk last night - Nos emborrachamos anoche
I get home in an hour and half
I got an eight in my examen -
She gets the bus everyday - Ella toma el colectivo todos los días
He doesn't get anything I told him - No entiende nada de lo que digo.
They going to get married the next year - Se van a casar el año que viene
